GULF; AUSTRALIA -- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; TANKERS; BLOCKADES; UNITED 
STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; FOOD SHORTAGES; HOSTAGES -- IRAQ; HOSTAGES 
-- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- FOREIGN POPULATIONS; KUWAIT -- FOREIGN POPULATIONS; 
