GULF; MILITARY STRATEGY; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- JAPAN; UNITED STATES 
-- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- JAPAN; JAPAN -- FOREIGN AID -- MIDDLE EAST 
</P>
