</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWSWIRE: NAMES IN THE NEWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Center Jesse Spinner, who played at Los Angeles Crenshaw High School and 
Grambling before joining an Austrian team last season, signed a one-year 
contract with the Dallas Mavericks. 
</P>
