daughter, Katie, watch planes from the observation deck of John Wayne airport. 
; Photo, Bettie Stevenson, manager of the terminal gift shop, will be out of 
work when old facility closes. GARY AMBROSE / Los Angeles Times; Photo, A 1989 
photo shows passengers boarding on portable stairs. Covered jetways replace 
stairs. ; Photo, A sign at the tiny gift shop at old terminal offers a bargain. 
