Chrysler Corp. renamed it ARCAD Inc. subsidiary, created as a 50-50 joint 
venture with The new name reflects the "JJ" code-name of a small sport-utility 
vehicle that the company the French auto maker Renault, as JJ International 
Automotive Corp., the U.S. company said. 
</P>
