<P>
New U.S. Boss at Saatchi: The revolving door among top executives at troubled 
Saatchi &amp; Saatchi Advertising is still spinning. After less than two years, 
Jonathan T. Hirst, 41, is out as president and chief executive of the 
British-based company's U.S. holdings. Martin Tucker, 67, general counsel for 
Saatchi in the United States, replaces him. 
