Icahn Buys Integrated Resources Unit: Carl C. Icahn won an auction in U.S. 
Bankruptcy Court for American Property Investors, a real estate holding company 
of New York-based Integrated Resources. Icahn bid $44-million for the company. 
The purchase represents an expansion into the real estate business for Icahn. 
